Requirements
  Python >= 2.5 

  Twisted >= 10.1.0

  Orbited >= 0.7
  
  Storm >= 0.16.0.0 
  
  Evoque >= 0.4 and Qpy >= 1.8
  
  pyyaml >= 3.08

Installation 

  * Gentoo
    Add DamnWidget overlay (https://github.com/DamnWidget/damnwidget-overlay) to your layman repos
    and then do as root:
    $ emerge -av goliat

  * Any
    As with other Python packages, the standard way of installing from source
    is:

      python setup.py install
